@startuml

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ArrowColor #2C3E50
skinparam ArrowThickness 2
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #2C3E50
skinparam RectangleFontSize 13

title Impact Analysis: Change Propagation Through Used-By

rectangle "Web Controller" as WC #FAFAFA
rectangle "Mobile Controller" as MC #FAFAFA
rectangle "API Gateway" as AG #FAFAFA
rectangle "**Order Service**" as OS #C8E6C9
rectangle "**Inventory Service**" as IS #C8E6C9
rectangle "  Payment Gateway  " as PG #BBDEFB

WC -down-> OS : <<uses>>
MC -down-> OS : <<uses>>
AG -down-> OS : <<uses>>
OS -down-> IS : <<uses>>
OS -down-> PG : <<uses>>

note as CHANGE #FFCDD2
  **Proposed Change:**
  Modify Payment Gateway
  interface
end note

CHANGE .right. PG

note right of OS #FFF9C4
  **Direct Impact**
  Order Service directly
  uses Payment Gateway
  → must be reviewed
end note

note right of WC #FFF9C4
  **Transitive Impact**
  All three controllers
  use Order Service
  → potentially affected
end note

note as SCOPE #E8F8F5
  **Impact Scope = 4 modules**
  Direct: Order Service
  Transitive: Web Controller,
  Mobile Controller, API Gateway
end note
@enduml
